			<h2><strong>PLATFORM</strong></h2>
<p>The New Museum Digital Archive was built using <a href="http://www.collectiveaccess.org" target="_ext">CollectiveAccess</a>, an open source, Web-based software application to catalog, manage, and publish museum and archival collections. The Digital Archive follows standardized archiving metadata structure (qualified Dublin Core). CollectiveAccess is free software released under the GNU Public License, version 2. CollectiveAccess and changes in code from the New Museum Digital Archive project are free and available to the public or other institutions.</p>

